  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Tormented Soul on Discord! (Links & Info section for link)</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/700c938a1b13dcec14ef0a99173a9f5c.poster.avif?t=1755985669\" width=800 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/700c938a1b13dcec14ef0a99173a9f5c.webm?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/700c938a1b13dcec14ef0a99173a9f5c.mp4?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Innovative AOE-centric Skill Based Action Combat—</strong>The combat in Tormented Soul is extremely intuitive, unique, satisfying, and smooth—with the feel of a third-person shooter brought to fantasy action combat. The combat has added nuance and attention to detail—with the quickswap weapon system utilizing mid-ability swap buffering, there is animation cancels for players to master double-ultimate combos, and above all there is a need to aim your abilities accurately.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Corrupted</strong> <strong>PvP. Partial loot—Corrupt items transfer in PvP—cleanse items at Florencia. </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.poster.avif?t=1755985669\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.webm?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.mp4?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ---Please check back later for new GIFs/Info due to new Open World mode patch!---  <br></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Innovative AOE-centric Skill Based Action Combat—</strong>The combat in Tormented Soul is extremely intuitive, unique, satisfying, and smooth—with the feel of a third-person shooter brought to fantasy action combat. The combat has added nuance and attention to detail—with the quickswap weapon system utilizing mid-ability swap buffering, there is animation cancels for players to master double-ultimate combos, and above all there is a need to aim your abilities accurately.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Corrupted</strong> <strong>PvP. Partial loot—Corrupt items transfer in PvP—cleanse items at Florencia. </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.poster.avif?t=1755985669\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.webm?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269360/extras/c61bfec6c3e82dec4133956242b88080.mp4?t=1755985669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ---Please check back later for new GIFs/Info due to new Open World mode patch!---  <br></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2>",
